{
  "_meta": {
    "vendor": "USCD",
    "format": "USCD native webhook event payload — verbatim as sent to Hub",
    "endpoint": "POST https://api-v3.hoodslyhub.com/v1/order/create",
    "endpoint_legacy_shim": "POST /wp-json/uscd/v1/order",
    "auth_header": "X-API-Key: {{USCD_API_KEY}}",
    "notes": [
      "USCD pushes webhook events — payload is wrapped in an event envelope: event, event_id, sent_at",
      "Address is in data.shipto using street1/street2/zip (not address_1/postcode)",
      "data.shipto.biz is the business/company name, data.shipto.attn is the recipient",
      "Line items are in data.order_lines[] using sku (not sku_code)",
      "accessorials control delivery options: residential, appointment, notification, liftgate",
      "purchase_order and sales_order are the USCD reference numbers",
      "ship_on becomes the estimated shipping date in Hub"
    ]
  },
